v0.42.0: stargaze mode

- new 'Stargaze' button + G key frees the camera to tilt up and pan across the night sky (constellations, galaxies, phasing moon, aurora, shooting stars)
- aims up-and-forward from the current view, slow auto-drift across the stars; restores the normal ground camera on exit
- creature-picking is disabled while gazing; combines with photo mode (H) for a pure sky view
